<concept id="concept_E8D43EB4494E41D2AB42D4A89396D1AB"
                    xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Distribution Media</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p><i><b>PENDING</b>: Distribution media for CMM 1.2 has not yet been defined; CMM 1.2 is in Beta status.</i></p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <p><ph conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> is distributed in the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> installation package. It contains the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> software and documentation for installing and configuring <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> in single mode and cluster mode. </p>
            <p>The package includes:<ul>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>setup.sh</codeph> script for setting up the <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> installer.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>Licenses</codeph> subdirectory:</p>
                        <p>License files of third-party software used by <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>Service</codeph> subdirectory:</p>
                        <p>Installation package for <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>, <codeph><ph
                                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                />-Service-1.2.0.tar.gz</codeph>. It provides the software and setup utilities required by the <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                /> Operator and the OpenStack Operator for installing <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                            /> in either single or cluster mode. </p>
                        <p><codeph>FJSVsvcmm-1.2.0-1.noarch.rpm</codeph> , an RPM required for checking version information.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>Manuals</codeph> subdirectory:</p>
                        <p>PDF manuals providing an overview of <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                />, as well as information directed to the tenant user, the OpenStack operator, and the <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> operator.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
